Subject: [PATCH 2/2] LLVM 22 compatibility (#2987)

* llvm_22.1.0

* add missing components

* fix LLVM 22 compatibility and add AVX10.1, AVX10.2

* update release notes, detect if `libLLVMDTLTO` exists

* relax gather_scatter test expectations for LLVM compatibility

* use LLVM_VERSION_MAJOR check for LLVM 22 masked intrinsics

---------

Co-authored-by: Christoffer Lerno <christoffer@aegik.com>
